{"tid":1593323,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"未成年市民於8.31被警察無差別襲擊 父代子告一哥","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:49:26.000Z","uid":123774,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96a13ceacdb4d29fa8887765d6153774c80ea317","tid":1593323,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"終於有人告<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31有市民自發到港島各區「行街」，其後演變成嚴重警民衝突。大批防暴警察及速龍小隊衝進港鐵太子站內車廂，以警棍無差別的毆打市民，造成多人受傷。一名當天在站內的未成年市民，由父親代表入稟區域法院，指稱當日遭警方毆打致受傷，控告警務處處長並提出索償。<br />\n<br />\n李姓原告由父親代表入稟，被告警務處處長由律政司代表。入稟狀指，原告今年8月31日於港鐵太子站內遭受被告、其僱員及或其代理人毆打及或疏忽對待，因而受傷，原告為此向被告申索，包括一般、特定賠償，以及法庭認為適合的加重及懲罰性賠償。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀未述明原告的詳細傷勢，亦未透露索償額，而區域法院最高申索額為300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCPI3161/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60082151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60082151&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9FYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=eee18881\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60082151&h=cc0f604d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60082151</a>"},{"pid":"34e1b4289879f901c1a7b286c4c5819aa351645b","tid":1593323,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"7f4db73466d4f6c7acd6aa655cf0801f1658d900","tid":1593323,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"係咪可以叫法庭判黨鐵出示cctv"},{"pid":"99d473b4ffa50b51986c4372aeb4fd68a7e5187a","tid":1593323,"uid":21340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"李爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd7a53cdf56525968d7fa7b2316daf9b9e807de","tid":1593323,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c50d6a358eeffd6dee0b3432cf836b25709a71","tid":1593323,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:41:06.000Z","msg":"sorry ,幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣工作]入黎揀個宣傳方法去做！重現69吹大雞！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593328\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593328</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1.網絡宣傳+airdrop</strong></span><br />\n最易，亦都有好多巴絲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦哂<br />\n大家可以幫手post 去 fb,ig,twitter, <span style=\"color: red;\">仲有香討等各大論壇！</span>講真上得連登大部分都了解黎緊有咩活動，但仲有一大班人玩開其他論壇， 我建議可以用洗連登式洗各論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2.各區連儂牆+各戶大廈𨋢口，洗樓</strong></span><br />\n連儂牆基本啦，唔洗多講，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以痴文宣係自己大廈𨋢口度，咁啲人等𨋢就睇到！</span> 最快靚正就痴係𨋢入邊，又或者攝係平時啲公告板入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以痴𨋢門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>3.痴各交通工具入邊</strong></span><br />\n開始有風險既一個做法，比人捉到會比人鬧，或觸犯唔知乜春例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以揀d 陰濕位痴<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如番工番學準備定一兩張文宣痴好雙面膠，臨落車先痴</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>4.痴文宣上自己身，番工番學做流動宣傳</strong></span><br />\n難，難在恥力不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一般人唔慣痴野上身比人用異目睇，不過為左香港， i do<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以痴係背脊或背囊，冇咁尷尬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>5. 擺街站，派傳單</strong></span><br />\n最難，但都係最有效接觸到唔同類型既人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有安全風險，最好約埋幾個一齊做，揀人流多，未入夜既時間，事半功倍</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少宣傳，多一個人做，效果雖然唔明顯，但如果多10萬個人做宣傳，個效果就好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手推，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另附少量文宣，岩用就用，唔岩去文宣tg 揀，大家整得好辛苦，要多多使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b901ce22562f36f48f3eded7e8cea1b3c6cd8d94","tid":1593323,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推到有完整cctv"},{"pid":"d559b135adb2d902a61b767c9cbea2b7dc341452","tid":1593323,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:44:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929 + 101 <span style=\"color: red;\">聲援新疆！</span></span>將香港抗爭運動推向成為全球性對抗極權革命！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592965</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IsDCpBPjDv0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIsDCpBPjDv0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=79f1a2bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">929<span style=\"color: gold;\">黑布蒙眼靜坐行動(舉標語) </span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集合地點：<br />\n929 sogo 門外 2pm集合</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: 